      "content": "Those skeptical arguments about regulation being used for corporate advantage are a valid political critique, but they do not negate the underlying technical risks. Scientifically, the concern about uncontrollable advanced AI is rooted in complex alignment problems—ensuring superintelligent systems share human intent. While some risks are theoretical, experts point to the compounding nature of these risks, making them a grounded, high-stakes concern for safety researchers.",
